Package gutek.repositories

package gutek.repositories
This package contains Spring Data JPA repositories, including:
  • Application user repository.
  • App Locale settings repository.
  • Card repository.
  • Repository for managing card revision registration.
  • Deck repository.
  • Deck statistics repository.
  • Revision algorithms repository.
  • Revision statistics counts repository.
